#. Tag: para
#: man-cxxmetric.1.docbook:35
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"cxxmetric counts lines of code, comment and blank space and calculates "
"various other statistics for each given source file. Source files must be in "
"C or C++."
msgstr ""
"cxxmetric broji linije koda, komentare i prazna mjesta i računa mnoge druge "
"statistike za svaki izvorni dokument.Izvorni dokumenti moraju biti u C  ili "
"u C++."

